<div class="insurance-banner">
  <div class="insurance-banner-inner container">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="insurance-banner-icon">
      <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
      <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/>
      <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
    </svg>
    <p class="insurance-banner-text">
      当院では現在<strong>マイナンバーカードの読み取りによる保険資格の確認ができません。</strong>健康保険証・資格確認書、またはマイナポータルの資格情報画面をお持ちください。
      <a href="/#insurance" class="insurance-banner-link">詳しくはこちら →</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .insurance-banner {
    background: #fdf2e6;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e8a04c;
    padding: 14px 0;
  }

  .insurance-banner-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .insurance-banner-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #c07020;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .insurance-banner-text {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .insurance-banner-text strong {
    color: #c05040;
  }

  .insurance-banner-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-left: 8px;
    color: #a36232;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .insurance-banner-link:hover {
    color: #8b4f28;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .insurance-banner-text {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }

    .insurance-banner-link {
      display: block;
      margin-left: 0;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
  }
</style>
